Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:36.48,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Her name is Amamiya Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.40,0:01:41.24,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,She's my childhood friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:44.22,def2,..KUNIMI..,0,0,0,,When she's with me, she \Nshows her strong-willed side...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.22,0:01:47.00,def2,..KUNIMI..,0,0,0,,...but in front of Hideo, whom she loves, she becomes an awfully attractive girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.04,0:01:57.03,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,But that's not supposed to be all there is to her.
