Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:12.47,def2,..KINE:...,0,0,0,,Koga.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:13.57,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,What is it ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:16.18,def2,..KINE:...,0,0,0,,Practice ended early.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.18,0:02:17.19,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.19,0:02:19.26,def2,..KINE:...,0,0,0,,You have time, right ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.26,0:02:20.80,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:25.73,def2,..KINE:...,0,0,0,,Let's go home together.\N I'll buy you a hot monja.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.73,0:02:27.50,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,I'm not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:34.25,def2,..COACH:..,0,0,0,,Do you want to go home together ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:36.70,def2,..KINE:...,0,0,0,,Um, well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.07,0:02:39.70,def2,..COACH:..,0,0,0,,Let's go home together, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:40.65,def2,..KINE:...,0,0,0,,What ? What ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:43.45,def2,..COACH:..,0,0,0,,You're going to treat \Nme to some monja ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:44.30,def2,..KINE:...,0,0,0,,What ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:45.70,def2,..COACH:..,0,0,0,,I'm Koga, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:46.50,def2,..KINE:...,0,0,0,,What ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:57.22,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Koga, which do you like better, takoyaki or imagawayaki ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:03.09,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,It's tasty !
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:07.70,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,If you're looking for cheap but good food, you should leave it to me, Noda Atsushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:19.40,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\frz282.5\pos(589.333,87.111)}Imagawayaki
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:12.20,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,He's been eating out a lot since elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:16.55,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,The soy-flour candy at that\N candy store in front of the school...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:19.00,def2,...NODA...,0,0,0,,That was the best ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:20.24,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:24.56,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,Hiro would put so many of them into his mouth at once that he'd choke on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.56,0:03:28.95,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,He kept wheezing, so the candy store lady called an ambulance one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:31.75,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,That happened ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.41,0:03:33.76,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:40.08,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Hey, is your elementary\N school far from here ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:42.01,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,No, it's just a ten-minute walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:43.58,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,I want to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:45.34,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,I don't want to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:52.72,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,Oh, I should show you the \Ngraduation totem pole that Hiro broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:53.70,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,What's that ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:58.25,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,There's also the wall that Hiro tried to jump over and failed when he was late for class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.47,0:04:00.84,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.88,0:04:07.66,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,I said I'm not going !
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:16.40,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:18.74,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,What was that ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:21.60,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,Hey, Hiro !
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:24.98,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,You're not coming, Kunimi ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:28.20,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,I guess I'll go.
