Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:45.85,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,According to him, he thought he could pull off a "daruma otoshi."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:48.26,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,That was a pure and innocent idea, appropriate for a child.
