Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:26.16,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,It feels small now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:35.24,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,This is where you two{Kunimi and Noda} \Nstarted playing baseball ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:36.08,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,Yeah.
