Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:55.29,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,We used to make throws\N from here to those iron bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:57.16,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,When you were in elementary school ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:06:00.20,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,We reached there when we \Nwere in fifth grade, right, Noda ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:04.50,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Even when you were\N little, you were amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:05.55,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,Shall we make a throw ?
