Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:56.40,def2,TACHIBANA:,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:04.45,def2,TACHIBANA:,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:06.31,def2,.PLAYERA:.,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:17.47,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Rehab is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:23.23,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Amamiya Hikari,\N thanks for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:25.81,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:38.60,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fscx177\fscy121\pos(170.667,473.778)}Sanpou Sports
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:41.43,def2,..COACH:..,0,0,0,,Tachibana !
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:48.05,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HF5F4ED&\fscx72\fscy70\frz349.5\pos(474.667,54.222)}Sanpou Sports
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:48.05,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\a3\c&H000000&\3c&HF5F4ED&\fscx71\fscy67\frz349.2\pos(391.111,94.222)}Reporter,\NAmamiya Takaaki
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:48.05,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HF5F4ED&\fscx73\fscy63\pos(240,144.889)\frz346}Tokyo,\NAdachi-ku,\NKobayashi\N0-00-0
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.38,0:08:48.03,def2,.AMAMIYA:.,0,0,0,,I'm Amamiya from Sanpou Sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:49.93,def2,TACHIBANA:,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:53.52,def2,TACHIBANA:,0,0,0,,Mr. Amamiya...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:59.32,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,A memory from a snowy day ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:04.28,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,I think that's what it is, \Nbut I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:06.55,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,A snowball fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:08.85,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:10.00,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,You made a snow hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:11.91,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,That's not it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:17.31,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,Is it about when we drew pictures in the snow with our pee ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:18.97,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,That's definitely not it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:23.15,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Is it about Hikari ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:28.38,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Um, well, it's probably nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:33.80,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,I hope it'll accumulate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:35.53,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,If it does, you might remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:39.72,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Moron ! We won't be\N able to practice if it does !
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:42.10,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,That's true.{ guess.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:49.21,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,But today will also be a \Nmemorable day, wrapped up in snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:52.40,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Really, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:08.01,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,That's what I said, \Nbut it bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:14.16,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Crap !
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:21.35,def2,.MOTHER:..,0,0,0,,Hiro, you have a phone call !
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:28.11,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}Hikari's essay ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:32.08,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,When Haruka mentioned \NHikari's name, I remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:36.00,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,Something about snow, and the elm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:39.02,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,She wrote something about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.02,0:10:40.40,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,That must be it !
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:43.14,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}Can't you find it in the \Ngraduation essay collection ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:47.77,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,I can't read mine because of the scribbles you made.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:51.99,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:56.50,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:11:00.50,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HF5F4ED&\fscx75\fscy66\pos(286.222,363.556)}Amamiya Hikari\N\NMemories of \NElementary School
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:10:59.60,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:06.10,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,This might be it. You remember that we buried a time capsule, right ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:10.57,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}Didn't we put "My Treasure" into it ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.57,0:11:11.42,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:18.41,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,You put a ball in. I put a cap in. \NAnd I think Hikari put her essay in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:21.80,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,Do you want to \Ndig it up and see it ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:26.75,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}Moron ! That's meant to \Nbe a present for future kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:28.38,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,Then there's only one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:34.20,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}If you want to know what's in that essay, you should just ask Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:38.64,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,It's nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:41.84,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,It's not worth asking her about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:43.12,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Just forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:47.05,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,Well, even if they're\N not the tastiest things...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.05,0:11:51.44,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,...you get nostalgic about cheap snacks and you somehow feel like eating them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:16.50,yamato,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H313275&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(293,151)}Aim for the Koushien
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.70,0:12:24.45,yamato,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H313275&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(309.333,157.333)}Aim for the Koushien
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:31.31,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}It's nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:34.61,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}It's not worth asking her about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:35.60,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}Just forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:48.30,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:51.16,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:56.05,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,You're playing pachinko again ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:57.98,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,What do you mean "again" ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:13:03.19,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,I always see you near a pachinko place or a bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.19,0:13:06.18,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,I've only seen you tending the store once or twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:08.34,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,That's not nice to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:10.40,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,I get up early in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:14.08,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,...open the boxes of books delivered to us, and display them in the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:19.51,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,And after everyone goes to sleep,\N I organize the receipts and do bookkeeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:21.49,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,Man, I'm so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:24.30,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Why don't you do all those things during the day...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:26.75,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,...when you're otherwise just dawdling around ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:29.54,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,Pachinko places would close, you know ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:32.97,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Pachinko places are open late, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.97,0:13:35.70,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,In the evening hours, \Nthe good slots are all taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:41.09,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Oh, well. Because you're hardly ever home, people think that you've left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:42.79,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.79,0:13:47.53,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Then do you know what Hikari's treasure\N was when she was in elementary school ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:55.11,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,Well, why don't you come to our\Nhouse for a cup of tea, for once ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.11,0:13:58.55,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,I always stop by your house.\NYou're just hardly ever there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:14:00.23,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,Really ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:06.50,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H88B7D6&\fscx178\fscy150\move(403.556,383.111,366.223,382.222,40,5420)}Amamiya
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:06.37,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Oh, how rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:09.28,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,You're such a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:11.76,def2,...MAN....,0,0,0,,What do you mean, \N"I always stop by your house" ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:13.90,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,"How rare," she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:15.80,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,I was talking about you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:17.06,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.51,0:14:19.46,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Oh, Uncle is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:22.78,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,Takaaki is here ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:24.37,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:29.95,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Takaaki is a newspaper reporter, right ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:34.57,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's going back to the\N main office in Tokyo next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:35.80,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:42.77,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,Hey, Hiro, come here !
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:44.65,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:46.74,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:50.55,def2,.TAKAAKI:.,0,0,0,,Hiro, you've grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:55.92,def2,.TAKAAKI:.,0,0,0,,What happened to baseball ? \NAre you still playing ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:57.47,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:14:59.16,def2,.TAKAAKI:.,0,0,0,,Which school do you go to ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:00.54,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,It's Senkawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:01.97,def2,.TAKAAKI:.,0,0,0,,Senkawa ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.13,0:15:14.45,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Their baseball club was \Nestablished just recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:16.77,def2,.TAKAAKI:.,0,0,0,,Oh, is that true ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:18.02,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:25.33,def2,.TAKAAKI:.,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, I just went to see Meiwa, the leading candidate for the Invitational.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.33,0:15:27.25,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,So he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:31.18,def2,.TAKAAKI:.,0,0,0,,That guy, Tachibana Hideo, lives up to his reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:35.06,def2,.TAKAAKI:.,0,0,0,,I think he's going to be a star player \Nwho will get people to come to the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:36.45,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,So he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:37.26,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:41.33,def2,.TAKAAKI:.,0,0,0,,He's smart, and he's thoughtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:43.45,def2,.TAKAAKI:.,0,0,0,,He'll do well in \Nprofessional baseball, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:48.69,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,If it's about Tachibana, it's \Nway easier to just ask Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:50.36,def2,.TAKAAKI:.,0,0,0,,Huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.36,0:15:56.00,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,I just remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:57.76,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Remembered what ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:16:02.50,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,The essay you wrote in elementary school, about your dream for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:13.40,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,It was to become a\N newspaper reporter, right ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:15.53,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Yeah, a sports reporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:16.30,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:45.70,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fscx52\fscy56\c&H000000&\3c&HF5F4ED&\pos(251.556,61.333)}Wednesday, May 21st
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:45.70,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HF5F4ED&\fscx91\fscy82\pos(363.556,85.333)}Class Newspaper
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:45.70,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HF5F4ED&\fscx67\fscy61\pos(302.222,193.778)}This Week's Kunimi and Noda
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:50.60,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HF5F4ED&}This Week's Kunimi and Noda\N{\c&H44449D&\3c&HF5F4ED&}He threw 70 meters !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:58.00,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Like that elm tree, I'd like to be\N someone who will never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:01.25,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Can it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:05.12,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Can it be what ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:07.45,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Is that still what you want to do ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:09.25,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,You think it's impossible, don't you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.02,0:17:11.00,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:14.76,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,I think you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:19.26,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,When I told Hide-chan about it, he didn't take me seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:24.19,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,It's because you never\N show your true self to Hideo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:25.41,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:30.90,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,When you're with him,\N you act like a docile, nice girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:38.45,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Hideo doesn't know how \Nstubborn or strong-willed you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:46.10,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Boys want to show their good sides when they're with girls, too, right ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:51.24,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,If you don't show him your true character from time to time, it'll be stressful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:52.46,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Oh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:57.41,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you're done playing the go-between ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:00.12,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:05.12,def2,.TAKAAKI:.,0,0,0,,Hikari and Tachibana Hideo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.12,0:18:06.50,def2,.MOTHER:..,0,0,0,,Are you surprised ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:13.12,def2,.TAKAAKI:.,0,0,0,,Well, I have no complaint about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:15.97,def2,.TAKAAKI:.,0,0,0,,But as a pair, \Nit feels a bit strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:18.00,def2,.MOTHER:..,0,0,0,,Is that a news reporter's intuition ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:21.13,def2,.TAKAAKI:.,0,0,0,,Well, it's not anything reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:25.72,def2,.TAKAAKI:.,0,0,0,,My image of Hikari is that of her when \Nshe was in elementary school, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:26.88,def2,.MOTHER:..,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:37.50,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:41.13,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}My treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:43.47,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}...is my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.97,0:18:48.80,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Memories are memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:53.78,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:57.86,def2,.FATHER:..,0,0,0,,Oh, he's home now ! \NHe's home now !
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:03.80,def2,.FATHER:..,0,0,0,,Hey, moronic son.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:06.51,def2,..FATHER..,0,0,0,,You have a phone call from the company president's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.38,0:19:09.45,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,What's up ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:11.00,def2,.FATHER:..,0,0,0,,Hey !
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:15.04,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,The snow is beautiful ? \NAre you a moron ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.68,0:19:21.26,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,All the powerhouse schools \Nhave indoor workout facilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:25.61,def2,..KUNIMI..,0,0,0,,If this weather continues, \Nthey'll get even further ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.87,0:19:30.14,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, we'll start to remove the snow from the{baseball} field in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:31.50,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,So get up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:33.70,def2,.FATHER:..,0,0,0,,Speak more politely...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.70,0:19:36.67,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,I can't wake up by myself, so come pick me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:38.40,def2,.FATHER:..,0,0,0,,What have you done...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:41.77,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Six o'clock ? \NMoron ! It's too early !
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:44.65,def2,.FATHER:..,0,0,0,,Honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:48.80,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess that sounds right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:49.81,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:55.83,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Huh ? What ? \NThe snow is beautiful ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.83,0:19:58.87,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,You're still talking about that ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:00.90,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,You have to live for the future ! \NFor the future !
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:31.45,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Like that elm tree, I want to be someone who'll never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:35.69,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,He remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:40.70,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,My treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:43.92,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,It is my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:48.40,def2,..HIKARI..,0,0,0,,When I see that elm tree in the schoolyard, I always feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:55.55,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,In snow or rain, that elm tree has always encouraged me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:21:00.73,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,That's why I want to\N be like that elm tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:09.53,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,I like baseball. I like how everyone works hard and plays the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:15.66,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,I want other people to know this feeling, so I'd like to be a sports reporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:20.38,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,I think that, if I work hard like that elm tree, my dream will someday come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:48.36,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,You think it's impossible, don't you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.36,0:21:51.15,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,No, I think you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.15,0:21:53.48,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Yup.
