Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.18,0:22:29.65,Karaoke Translation op,..EDSONG:..,0,0,0,,{\pos(307.556,464)}...I want to get past a hardship like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.88,0:22:37.45,Karaoke Translation op,..EDSONG:..,0,0,0,,{\pos(304,464.889)}Like you, I run up the pedestrian bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.63,0:22:45.88,Karaoke Translation op,..EDSONG:..,0,0,0,,{\pos(309.333,464.889)}...keeping up with the sunny sky, I want to feel courageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.38,0:22:52.60,Karaoke Translation op,..EDSONG:..,0,0,0,,{\pos(305.778,463.111)}"How does he keep such a nice facial expression ?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.92,0:23:01.23,Karaoke Translation op,..EDSONG:..,0,0,0,,{\pos(297.778,463.111)}I thought with frustration, when I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:04.53,Karaoke Translation op,..EDSONG:..,0,0,0,,{\pos(304,462.222)}"I'm definitely glad we met."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.22,0:23:08.35,Karaoke Translation op,..EDSONG:..,0,0,0,,{\pos(307.556,461.333)}Let's stay strong and move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.08,0:23:12.08,Karaoke Translation op,..EDSONG:..,0,0,0,,{\pos(321.778,462.222)}When I'm by myself I notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:16.03,Karaoke Translation op,..EDSONG:..,0,0,0,,{\pos(308.444,464.889)}...that, beyond this dazzling feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.86,0:23:19.83,Karaoke Translation op,..EDSONG:..,0,0,0,,{\pos(311.111,465.778)}...yesterday, today, and tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:24.08,Karaoke Translation op,..EDSONG:..,0,0,0,,{\pos(312.889,464.889)}...there are more and more smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.58,0:23:27.53,Karaoke Translation op,..EDSONG:..,0,0,0,,{\pos(305.778,464)}Just by looking at you, see ?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.18,0:23:31.63,Karaoke Translation op,..EDSONG:..,0,0,0,,{\pos(311.111,464)}My eyes will look kinder.
